org.gradoop.storage.impl.hbase.handler

Class HBaseGraphHeadHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.storage.impl.hbase.handler.HBaseElementHandler
      • org.gradoop.storage.impl.hbase.handler.HBaseGraphHeadHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ElementHandler, GraphHeadHandler

    public class HBaseGraphHeadHandler
extends HBaseElementHandler
implements GraphHeadHandler
    Used to read/write EPGM graph data from/to a HBase table. Graph data in HBase: |---------|-------------|----------| | row-key | meta | data | |---------|-------------|----------| | "0" | label | k1 | k2 | | |-------------|----------| | | "Community" | v1 | v2 | |---------|-------------|----------|
